Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:14.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}正視著膽怯的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:22.77,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}依然無法理解地畏懼著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:24.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}背後的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:31.72,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}此刻映照在現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.83,0:01:36.83,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}描繪了數片天空的此處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:38.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}一定是在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:44.37,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}亂我脆弱心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:50.08,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}乘著夢想高飛身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:52.94,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}無論有任何不安糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:54.98,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}都掙脫前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:59.42,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}將沉睡著的小小的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:01.64,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}擴展開來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:03.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}意識到弱小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:10.40,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}只要有你在 黑暗的世界 也能一直堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:16.16,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}用沉眠許久的心 永遠堅強
